  "detailed_description": "Midnight Acres was built using Unreal Engine 5 and features a beautiful and dynamic day and night system.<br><u><strong>Daytime Gameplay</strong></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/39622da41129f4a16cade37fdb656c0d.avif?t=1698264723\" width=380 height=214 /></span><br>During the daytime, build and expand your farm and engage in casual and relaxing building & management.<br>Gather resources to upgrade your farm and defenses.<br>Relax by exploring the world for treasures, fishing in various ponds and underground lakes, managing your farm, and more!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/518ba20be4805f39862cef2154d9082c.poster.avif?t=1698264723\" width=380 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/518ba20be4805f39862cef2154d9082c.webm?t=1698264723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/518ba20be4805f39862cef2154d9082c.mp4?t=1698264723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><u><strong>Nighttime Gameplay</strong></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/f71aab4f6aff36f9c41ebfe22615e51b.avif?t=1698264723\" width=380 height=214 /></span><br>When night falls, you must push back hordes of enemies trying to destroy you and your farm.<br>Engage in intense FPS combat with various weapons.<br>Use tower-defense elements to place and upgrade turrets and defenses for your farm.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/a9ab4215d2263d6d8f61217d81b8c19a.poster.avif?t=1698264723\" width=380 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/a9ab4215d2263d6d8f61217d81b8c19a.webm?t=1698264723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/a9ab4215d2263d6d8f61217d81b8c19a.mp4?t=1698264723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><u><strong><br>Exploration</strong></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/cf5815954be8cc2be5cf48235c78ec7a.poster.avif?t=1698264723\" width=380 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/cf5815954be8cc2be5cf48235c78ec7a.webm?t=1698264723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/cf5815954be8cc2be5cf48235c78ec7a.mp4?t=1698264723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore a vast world with a sprawling cave system and rare collectibles... but beware. <br>Monsters constantly patrol the underground and guard the most valuable treasures.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/bf0ee13ef83ca0dd22e0528144335b7a.poster.avif?t=1698264723\" width=380 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/bf0ee13ef83ca0dd22e0528144335b7a.webm?t=1698264723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/bf0ee13ef83ca0dd22e0528144335b7a.mp4?t=1698264723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Midnight Acres was built using Unreal Engine 5 and features a beautiful and dynamic day and night system.<br><u><strong>Daytime Gameplay</strong></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/39622da41129f4a16cade37fdb656c0d.avif?t=1698264723\" width=380 height=214 /></span><br>During the daytime, build and expand your farm and engage in casual and relaxing building & management.<br>Gather resources to upgrade your farm and defenses.<br>Relax by exploring the world for treasures, fishing in various ponds and underground lakes, managing your farm, and more!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/518ba20be4805f39862cef2154d9082c.poster.avif?t=1698264723\" width=380 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/518ba20be4805f39862cef2154d9082c.webm?t=1698264723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/518ba20be4805f39862cef2154d9082c.mp4?t=1698264723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><u><strong>Nighttime Gameplay</strong></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/f71aab4f6aff36f9c41ebfe22615e51b.avif?t=1698264723\" width=380 height=214 /></span><br>When night falls, you must push back hordes of enemies trying to destroy you and your farm.<br>Engage in intense FPS combat with various weapons.<br>Use tower-defense elements to place and upgrade turrets and defenses for your farm.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/a9ab4215d2263d6d8f61217d81b8c19a.poster.avif?t=1698264723\" width=380 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/a9ab4215d2263d6d8f61217d81b8c19a.webm?t=1698264723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/a9ab4215d2263d6d8f61217d81b8c19a.mp4?t=1698264723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><u><strong><br>Exploration</strong></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/cf5815954be8cc2be5cf48235c78ec7a.poster.avif?t=1698264723\" width=380 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/cf5815954be8cc2be5cf48235c78ec7a.webm?t=1698264723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/cf5815954be8cc2be5cf48235c78ec7a.mp4?t=1698264723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore a vast world with a sprawling cave system and rare collectibles... but beware. <br>Monsters constantly patrol the underground and guard the most valuable treasures.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/bf0ee13ef83ca0dd22e0528144335b7a.poster.avif?t=1698264723\" width=380 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/bf0ee13ef83ca0dd22e0528144335b7a.webm?t=1698264723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2536420/extras/bf0ee13ef83ca0dd22e0528144335b7a.mp4?t=1698264723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
